channel.title: Bands?
channel.description:
Hey guys!
I need some new bands! I'm running out of them! Here is a list of what I already listen to (no particular order): 1. Falling In Reverse 2. Escape the Fate 3. blessthefall 4. Motionless In White 5. The Word Alive 6. Slipknot 7. Blink 182 8. Green Day 9. Black Veil Brides 10. A Day To Remember 11. KoRn 12. We Came As Romans 13. A Skylit Drive 14. Sum 41 15. System Of A Down 16. The Offspring 17. 3 Days Grace 18. 3 Doors Down 19. Bullet For My Valentine 20. Good Charlotte 21. Drowning Pool 22. Skillet 23. Evenesance 24. Black Tide 25. AFI 26. Fallout Boy 27. Angels and Airwaves 28. +44 29. Hollywood Undead 30. Breathe Carolina 31. Chunk! No, Captain Chunk! 32. The Killers
Thanks guys!
